@startuml UC16_Sequence
title UC16: 设置选课规则 - 顺序图

actor "教务处" as AA
boundary "规则配置界面" as RuleForm
control "选课控制类" as EnrollCtrl
entity "CourseRule" as Rule
entity "Course" as Course

AA -> RuleForm : 配置名额、先修课等逻辑
RuleForm -> EnrollCtrl : saveRules(courseId, rulesData)
EnrollCtrl -> Rule : createOrUpdateRule(rulesData)
Rule --> EnrollCtrl : success
EnrollCtrl -> Course : bindRule(ruleId)
EnrollCtrl --> RuleForm : 设置生效提示
@enduml
